啦..我唔會出來交收的了..之後果幾個賣家即刻俾劣評我..嘿..班死毒男真係呢...我果刻完全feel到佢地酸到出汁啦....我訓前打左俾佢..不過佢無聽電話...可能訓左..我sd左個sms俾佢,同佢講miss you;) good night...之後佢sd左個sms俾我話 : ok thx..... <br />\n<br />\n嘻嘻嘻...雖然尋晚用左成份糧..不過ok la....拍拖緊係咁架啦....下次出嚟問埋佢個名同問佢幾歲先... 祝大家都搵到自己愛的人呀! 加油豬唷 ;)"},{"pid":"4585daba1791b68edf124f4a5177fc481398059b","tid":457283,"uid":42369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T11:01:42.000Z","msg":"原文已經係 11 年，搵唔返原 post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2093146fe7d5354ee136f5016b32f2789c6a8ff7","tid":457283,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T11:08:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原文已經係 11 年，搵唔返原 post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我一直都係單身"},{"pid":"7ffa000eed4290cc62f9e477462dfc534cdc3a5b","tid":457283,"uid":121473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T11:18:04.000Z","msg":"美心西餅改得幾好笑"},{"pid":"ef19823c561d2935615303f39260de46c43bc2ee","tid":457283,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T15:47:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eea1baf9680d50b09f4e988c23d06b94e082b4aa","tid":457283,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T16:45:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70626d68738162ce5ec5d07602250734f0548ed6","tid":457283,"uid":156820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T16:48:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51bf90b7a88315609ec81e14146f3cb2891d8a42","tid":457283,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11